<%- include('partials/header') %>

<div class="home-container">
    <section class="story-section">
        <h1>My Favorite Cooking Experience</h1>
        <div class="story-content">
            <p>
                When I think of cooking, the first thing that always comes to mind is going to my grandmother's house every week to help cook dinner. At first, being the grumpy kid I was, I was upset to be pulled away from my games and shows, but when I got into the kitchen, with the sweet smells in the air and family all around, I couldn't help but forget it quickly after starting. So cooking will always hold a special place in my heart and stomach because no meal tastes better than one you made yourself.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="favorites-section">
        <h2>My Top 5 Favorite Foods</h2>
        <div class="favorites-list">
            <div class="favorite-item">
                <span class="number">1</span>
                <span class="food">Banh Mi</span>
            </div>
            <div class="favorite-item">
                <span class="number">2</span>
                <span class="food">Chicken Sandwiches</span>
            </div>
            <div class="favorite-item">
                <span class="number">3</span>
                <span class="food">Taro Poundcake</span>
            </div>
            <div class="favorite-item">
                <span class="number">4</span>
                <span class="food">Beef Stroganoff</span>
            </div>
            <div class="favorite-item">
                <span class="number">5</span>
                <span class="food">My Dad's Chili</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>

<style>
.home-container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 40px 20px;
}

.story-section {
    margin-bottom: 50px;
    background: white;
    padding: 30px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

.story-section h1 {
    color: #2c3e50;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    font-size: 2.2em;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #e74c3c;
    padding-bottom: 10px;
}

.story-content p {
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #34495e;
    font-size: 1.1em;
    text-align: justify;
}

.favorites-section {
    background: white;
    padding: 30px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

.favorites-section h2 {
    color: #2c3e50;
    margin-bottom: 25px;
    font-size: 1.8em;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #3498db;
    padding-bottom: 10px;
}

.favorites-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 15px;
}

.favorite-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 15px;
    background: #f8f9fa;
    border-radius: 8px;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease;
}

.favorite-item:hover {
    transform: translateX(10px);
    background: #e8f4f8;
}

.number {
    background: #3498db;
    color: white;
    width: 30px;
    height: 30px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-right: 15px;
}

.food {
    color: #2c3e50;
    font-size: 1.1em;
}

@media (max-width: 600px) {
    .home-container {
        padding: 20px 15px;
    }

    .story-section h1 {
        font-size: 1.8em;
    }

    .favorites-section h2 {
        font-size: 1.5em;
    }
}
</style>

